# WarriorQueen7Capital_307443db (line 59476)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_307443db:
    # "The flanks on each far end of her army began to move forward."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_aa9d39c4 (line 59477)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_aa9d39c4:
    # "Wrapping around the center, they closed off the only escape that had been available to the Tribesmen."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_54eede1a (line 59478)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_54eede1a:
    # "Sarah watched as less then a few dozen Tribesmen realized what was happening and managed to escape the encirclement."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_25391e97 (line 59479)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_25391e97:
    # "The others, too lost in the frenzy of battle, did not retreat."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d3bf98e0 (line 59480)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d3bf98e0:
    # "The flanking units, mostly spearmen, had not yet seen battle and were eager for it."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_427e659f (line 59481)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_427e659f:
    # "Attacking the Tribesmen from behind, they found easy targets that were exhausted and caught by surprise."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d1cb00a8 (line 59482)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d1cb00a8:
    # "With heavy shields and long spears, even the common Rosannan footsoldier found it easy to kill these sons of war."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_52c61b1b (line 59483)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_52c61b1b:
    # "Pressed on all sides, surrounded, the Tribesmen continued to fight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5c410a93 (line 59484)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5c410a93:
    # "But their position had deteriorated so quickly that even they struggled to adapt."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1acaaa0f (line 59485)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1acaaa0f:
    # "While each of them was reduced to fighting as a single warrior, her army moved as one."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_41b28ba0 (line 59486)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_41b28ba0:
    # "The advancing Rosannan army pushed the Tribesmen together from all sides."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b8d0c38b (line 59487)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b8d0c38b:
    # "Their great advantage, their horses, turned meaningless in the frenzy of such a close melee."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_435a15a8 (line 59488)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_435a15a8:
    # "Sarah smiled as she saw the core of the Tribesmen formation shrink."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_99505fc9 (line 59489)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_99505fc9:
    # "One by one, layer by layer, her army took the Tribesmen forces apart."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a00b0bc5 (line 59490)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a00b0bc5:
    # "They had gambled a lot on the hope that they might kill her and break apart her army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0a51abb3 (line 59491)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0a51abb3:
    # "But they had fallen short."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d7a042a4 (line 59492)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d7a042a4:
    # "And in war, there was no partial victory."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c7a4b8fe (line 59493)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c7a4b8fe:
    # s "You!"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_900e14b5 (line 59494)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_900e14b5:
    # "Sarah called another messenger over."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_39825d58 (line 59495)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_39825d58:
    # s "Report along the line, finish up the last of the Tribesmen, then reposition to move on the capital."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a83593ab (line 59496)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a83593ab:
    # s "Also, instruct the engineers to keep firing, I want to see the city wall crumble."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_72356434 (line 59497)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_72356434:
    # "Scout" "Yes, Commander!"
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d3f3834b (line 59498)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d3f3834b:
    # "The young man rushed off along the length of the line, spreading her instructions as fast as he could manage."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_01501e7b (line 59499)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_01501e7b:
    # "In little time at all, the last of the Tribesmen were put to death."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8fd4a367 (line 59500)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8fd4a367:
    # "Once the victory had become clear, a mad zeal seemed to spread through the formation."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_153c5fbf (line 59501)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_153c5fbf:
    # "No longer were they hesitant for war. They were hungry for it."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2d112470 (line 59502)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2d112470:
    # "Sarah heard them sing out their battle songs in eager anticipation for marching on the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6357ce27 (line 59503)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6357ce27:
    # "They had feared the Tribesmen, as well they should have, but now they learned they were as mortal as any other man."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_11b7780a (line 59504)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_11b7780a:
    # "They could be broken."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_776fbfaf (line 59505)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_776fbfaf:
    # "Sarah watched her army fall back into formation."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_adcd42b7 (line 59506)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_adcd42b7:
    # "Overhead, she saw the boulders of the trebuchets, flying across the sky, striking the outer walls of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a6328fb8 (line 59507)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a6328fb8:
    # "Larges plumes of dust rose up."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1fe3b880 (line 59508)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1fe3b880:
    # "Stones, scattering, walls breaking, the violent roar of the siege."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c770f3f1 (line 59509)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c770f3f1:
    # "Sarah looked at one of her officers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5279573b (line 59510)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5279573b:
    # s "What is the situation with the Tribesmen?"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8b2b1b37 (line 59511)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8b2b1b37:
    # "Officer" "This attack was a large portion of their forces, but it wasn't all of them."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7470d139 (line 59512)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7470d139:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_10542f81 (line 59513)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_10542f81:
    # s "How many remain?"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_efeb7115 (line 59514)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_efeb7115:
    # "Officer" "Hard to say, they're hiding behind their walls."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ecde3e0f (line 59515)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ecde3e0f:
    # "Officer" "Best estimate, maybe less than five-thousand."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c1fb4a9b (line 59516)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c1fb4a9b:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ac326baf (line 59517)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ac326baf:
    # "A sizeable force, but far fewer than she had in her own army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3c33f6da (line 59518)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3c33f6da:
    # "Still, when she moved into the city, it would be a brutal slog."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_38cd4c26 (line 59519)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_38cd4c26:
    # "Block-by-block, she would have to fight her way through the city. Attacks could come from any direction."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2cb6de5b (line 59520)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2cb6de5b:
    # "And the march to Castle Reinmeer was long."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_346f6049 (line 59521)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_346f6049:
    # "Then there was the Castle itself, no easy target itself."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_36ad0f11 (line 59522)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_36ad0f11:
    # "Still, it had to be done."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_92944cd7 (line 59523)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_92944cd7:
    # "Sarah watched the walls of the city until finally a large boulder struck true."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_cbf7fa13 (line 59524)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_cbf7fa13:
    # "The integrity of the entire length of the wall gave out all at once."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8f4c1549 (line 59525)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8f4c1549:
    # "Along the rest of the wall, Sarah saw other gaps emerge. Even the city gate seemed close to collapsing."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0966ba92 (line 59532)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0966ba92:
    # "Sarah grabbed the horn that was tied to her waist."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_80410002 (line 59533)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_80410002:
    # "She drew in as much air as she could, filling her lungs, and brought the horn to her lips."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ac99047b (line 59534)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ac99047b:
    # "Exhaling with great force, she let out a titanous blast from the horn."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_aa1cba29 (line 59535)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_aa1cba29:
    # "The deep, pounding sound seemed to reverberate into her bones."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ca9c4b04 (line 59536)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ca9c4b04:
    # "All at once, her army began to march, advancing on the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_17ec66a4 (line 59537)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_17ec66a4:
    # "Sarah lowered the horn and watched in awe at the sheer size of her army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ca406620 (line 59538)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ca406620:
    # "Remaining near the rear, she advanced along with her army, staying wary of any other surprise attacks."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4584a379 (line 59539)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4584a379:
    # "Her army could win the battle, but if she died the blow to morale could undo much of their advantage."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2920f711 (line 59540)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2920f711:
    # "She didn't enjoy letting others risk their lives on her account, but she also knew she wasn't just one person anymore."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c53f0c83 (line 59541)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c53f0c83:
    # "Looking upon her home, she knew she was becoming so much more."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_983079bb (line 59542)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_983079bb:
    # "The army crossed the field."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e2638889 (line 59543)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e2638889:
    # "A few arrows fell on them as they advanced, but the large volley she had expected did not come."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_dd3876be (line 59544)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_dd3876be:
    # "The Tribesmen were experienced in war, but sieges were something they had far less experience with."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_959185f4 (line 59545)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_959185f4:
    # "Least of all, defending from a siege."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a39b8ff1 (line 59546)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a39b8ff1:
    # "It was then perhaps no surprise they had failed to prepare as well as they could have."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_64a3d871 (line 59547)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_64a3d871:
    # "As they neared the walls of the city, the gaps were large enough for her soldiers to advance safely."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_dd145e99 (line 59554)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_dd145e99:
    # "Her army moved into the city, passing through the damaged sections of the wall."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7a153cdd (line 59555)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7a153cdd:
    # "They were hardly more than a few steps in when the Tribesmen began their attack."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_228fb4ea (line 59556)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_228fb4ea:
    # "Using the narrow streets of the capital to their advantage, they hoped to compensate for their smaller numbers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4983bf88 (line 59557)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4983bf88:
    # "Arrows, shot from windows and rooftops."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4cf9ccfa (line 59558)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4cf9ccfa:
    # "Small groups, carrying out cavalry charges, hitting and running, only to dissapear in some side-street."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_49158699 (line 59559)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_49158699:
    # "They were trying to bleed her army out."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_88ab2916 (line 59560)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_88ab2916:
    # "But on her orders, her army kept advancing."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_33bdd8fd (line 59561)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_33bdd8fd:
    # "Sarah knew that with her numbers, her advantage was too significant."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_63cc0798 (line 59562)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_63cc0798:
    # "And so, despite the ongoing attacks from the Tribesmen, her army advanced deeper and deeper into the capital."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_65406965 (line 59563)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_65406965:
    # "As they all slowly passed through the broken walls, the streets of the city began to swell with soldiers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5bf3e236 (line 59564)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5bf3e236:
    # "Where at first the Tribesmen had been able to attack and dissapear into small streets, now Sarah's soldiers covered every angle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1ea7b8cb (line 59565)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1ea7b8cb:
    # "More and more of them flooded every part of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_dac6410e (line 59566)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_dac6410e:
    # "And with each street and square lost, the Tribesmen were pushed back into a smaller part of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f8f0dba4 (line 59567)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f8f0dba4:
    # "Already, Sarah could hear the cries of joy from the citizens, locked in their houses."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e6892d72 (line 59568)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e6892d72:
    # "As the Tribesmen lost ground, they found themselves increasingly concentrated into smaller and smaller spaces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_357ba2f6 (line 59569)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_357ba2f6:
    # "Their hit-and-run tactics were increasingly becoming futile."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d152f712 (line 59570)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d152f712:
    # "When they did attack now, they did so in larger numbers. More regular fighting."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_02298b71 (line 59571)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_02298b71:
    # "But that kind of fighting took its toll."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1819ad47 (line 59572)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1819ad47:
    # "It took its toll on both sides, but the Tribesmen did not have the numbers to spare for such a grinding conflict."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_aff9191f (line 59573)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_aff9191f:
    # "Sarah watched as their numbers dwindled."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_24624560 (line 59574)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_24624560:
    # "How with each passing moment, the Tribesmen fell back further, surrendering more ground."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_fb241f34 (line 59575)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fb241f34:
    # "By now, most of the city had been liberated."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3552f042 (line 59576)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3552f042:
    # "And the only place to fall back to for the Tribesmen, was the Castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2ba84a77 (line 59577)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2ba84a77:
    # "Sarah pressed her forces on, giving pursuit to the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_87cb8a49 (line 59578)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_87cb8a49:
    # "Finally, they relented and retreated all the way into the castle proper."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_44957d36 (line 59579)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_44957d36:
    # "Letting the gate fall shut behind them, they withdrew to their last and final position."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_fbbea9d9 (line 59580)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fbbea9d9:
    # "Sarah watched as their haggard forces tried to set up their last defense."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_03b5c991 (line 59581)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_03b5c991:
    # "Her own forces had been wounded, but for the most part, her army was still plenty able to keep on the fight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2f69279e (line 59582)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2f69279e:
    # "It was the Tribesmen that had ran out of steam."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b3b3e236 (line 59583)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b3b3e236:
    # "The central road of the city that led up to the Castle was the most direct route of attack."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8935f252 (line 59584)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8935f252:
    # "It would also be the quickest way to end this."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0b2bdb94 (line 59585)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0b2bdb94:
    # s "Send up the vanguard, have them take the castle gates. Once they're open, move up the rest of our forces."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_28ec2a43 (line 59586)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_28ec2a43:
    # "As ordered, Sarah watched her vanguard unit advance on the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_37aa6a0a (line 59587)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_37aa6a0a:
    # "The vanguard consisted of the best soldiers from her mercenary company and Rosannan Knights that had survived The Fall."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0bbce6a3 (line 59588)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0bbce6a3:
    # "Her most experienced soldiers, they would make for more than a decent match to the Tribesmen."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_414d6ab1 (line 59589)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_414d6ab1:
    # "As they moved on the castle gates, the Tribesmen tried to stop their advance by firing arrows."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_40593f41 (line 59590)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40593f41:
    # "But the heavy plated armor and large shields of the vanguard unit meant that not a single arrow found purchase."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b1815072 (line 59591)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b1815072:
    # "Reaching the castle gates, they brought out their siege axes and got to work."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_01ab309d (line 59592)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_01ab309d:
    # "With each swing, they chipped away at the large, solid wood door that blocked the entrance into the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c0b1dc5a (line 59593)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c0b1dc5a:
    # "The gates of Castle Reinmeer were solid, but even they could not endure forever."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bc1f4aa0 (line 59594)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bc1f4aa0:
    # "Meanwhile, so close to the gate, the Tribesmen could no longer properly fire their arrows, leaving the vanguard to hack away."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3cc3dfb1 (line 59595)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3cc3dfb1:
    # "Eventually, Sarah saw the door splinter."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3c24d463 (line 59596)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3c24d463:
    # "A hole, large enough for maybe two men to move through."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7b53e1fa (line 59597)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7b53e1fa:
    # "Without wasting a moment, they did."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_648e1b3a (line 59598)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_648e1b3a:
    # "On the other side, they found the Tribesmen waiting for them, attacking as they tried to move through."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e6a6f4c2 (line 59599)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e6a6f4c2:
    # "At first, the vanguard struggled, but with each man that moved through, they were able to push the Tribesmen back further."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e4ed4212 (line 59600)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e4ed4212:
    # "Before long, they had secured their position on the other end of the door and pushed the Tribesmen back into the Castle square."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_80737c96 (line 59601)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_80737c96:
    # "Rather than advance further, the vanguard seized the Castle gate."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4503b487 (line 59602)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4503b487:
    # "Pulling on the winch, they activated the machinery that had held the gates closed."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3e4f79f9 (line 59603)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3e4f79f9:
    # "They swung open with a deep and heavy thud."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4d6570d5 (line 59604)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4d6570d5:
    # "Sarah heard her own army scream out in celebration as they saw that the final obstacle to their victory had been thrown open."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_aa2a0a57 (line 59605)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_aa2a0a57:
    # "Before she could even issue the command, she saw her soldiers running up the road towards the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ec3ff921 (line 59606)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ec3ff921:
    # "Each was eager not to be denied their share of the glory of this day."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_63bf1f71 (line 59607)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_63bf1f71:
    # "The vanguard fell back, allowing the core of the army to move into the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b391da50 (line 59608)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b391da50:
    # "The Tribesmen fought bravely, but their numbers had dwindled so far that they could no longer mount a proper defense."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5e32ef5f (line 59609)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5e32ef5f:
    # "Sarah's forces moved through the castle like a torrential surge, pushing through the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d01d6f69 (line 59610)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d01d6f69:
    # "It was a battle for only a moment. Then it was a slaughter."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d1ed68b9 (line 59617)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d1ed68b9:
    # "Sarah entered the castle when most of the fighting had been settled."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c3b14a2b (line 59618)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c3b14a2b:
    # "All about, she saw the bodies of the Tribesmen sprawled. Hacked up. Blood smeared."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7389222f (line 59619)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7389222f:
    # "Here and there, some of her own soldiers were being treated for injuries of their own."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bc16c323 (line 59620)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bc16c323:
    # "A loud cheer rose up from the soldiers as they watched Sarah enter the castle grounds."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d88ce22b (line 59621)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d88ce22b:
    # "She raised her own fist in the air, triumphant."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_43a2b7d3 (line 59622)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_43a2b7d3:
    # "She felt her own heart pounding in her chest at the sight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8aae1c26 (line 59623)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8aae1c26:
    # "As her eyes fell on her ancestral home, the memories flooded back to her."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0ca7abd1 (line 59624)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0ca7abd1:
    # "And she was caught for a brief moment by a feeling she had lost for years."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_fb9a41f2 (line 59625)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fb9a41f2:
    # "Home."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_acf4656b (line 59626)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_acf4656b:
    # "She felt at home."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e3bf2593 (line 59627)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e3bf2593:
